.TH MILSPEC-CONTROL 1 "2025-10-11" "Dell MIL-SPEC Tools 1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
milspec-control \- Dell MIL-SPEC platform control utility

.SH SYNOPSIS
.B milspec-control
.RI [ COMMAND ]
.RI [ OPTIONS ]

.SH DESCRIPTION
.B milspec-control
provides an interactive menu-driven interface and command-line control
for Dell MIL-SPEC platform features including Mode 5 security, DSMIL
devices, and system monitoring.

.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B status
Display comprehensive system status
.TP
.B devices
List all DSMIL devices and their status
.TP
.B security
Show security configuration and Mode 5 level
.TP
.B monitor
Launch real-time monitoring dashboard
.TP
.B test
Run system functionality tests
.TP
.B emergency
Trigger emergency procedures (requires confirmation)

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-i ", " \-\-interactive
Launch interactive menu (default if no command)
.TP
.BR \-c ", " \-\-color
Enable colored output
.TP
.BR \-q ", " \-\-quiet
Suppress informational messages
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Display help message

.SH INTERACTIVE MODE
When launched without arguments, presents a menu:

.RS
1. View System Status
.br
2. View DSMIL Devices
.br
3. View Security Configuration
.br
4. Launch Monitoring Dashboard
.br
5. Run System Tests
.br
6. Emergency Procedures
.br
0. Exit
.RE

.SH EXAMPLES
.PP
Interactive mode:
.RS
milspec-control
.RE

.PP
Quick status check:
.RS
milspec-control status
.RE

.PP
List all devices:
.RS
milspec-control devices --verbose
.RE

.PP
Launch monitoring:
.RS
milspec-control monitor
.RE

